  <text>
      <body>
        

        <div xml:id="Whatever else you do"> 
          <interpGrp type="Happiness">
            <interp ana="#form" type="free">free</interp>
            <interp ana="#tone" type="happy">happy</interp>
            <interp ana="#topic" type="love">love</interp>
            <interp ana="#topic" type="society">society</interp>
          </interpGrp>
             <lg>
          <l>Whatever else you do or forbear,</l>
          <l>impose upon yourself the task of hapiness;</l>
          <l>and now and then abandon yourself</l>
          <l>to the joy of laughter. </l>
          <l/>
          <l>And however much you condemn</l>
          <l>the evil in the world, remember that the</l>
          <l>world is not all evil; that somewhere</l>
          <l>children are at play, as you yourself in the</l>
          <l>old days; that women still find joy</l>
          <l>in the stalwart hearts of men; </l>
        </lg>
        <lg>
          <l>And that men, treading with restless feet</l>
          <l>their many paths, may yet find refuge</l>
          <l>from the storms of the world in the cheerful</l>
          <l>house of love. </l>
        </lg>
            </div>
        
      </body>
